    {
      "text": "High buildings like those pictured on the next page are being put up in more and more great cities today in greater and greater numbers. They are apartment houses, which sometimes have hundreds of different families living under one roof. There may be as many as twenty or thirty floors in one apartment house, with homes for fifteen or twenty families on a floor.",
